{"tid":645523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國工程院院士：微軟故意放任Windows盜版 反過來說中國人小偷","createTime":"2018-04-28T08:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T09:49:05.000Z","uid":10338,"like":456,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae26225c588b27237fc97d4d294cb078e364a12","tid":645523,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"4月24日，中國工程院院士倪光南接受參訪時，發表了對微軟的Windows盜版系統的看法。他表示，微軟故意放任的Windows盜版，使中國人沒機會發展自己的操作系統。小偷。&ldquo;倪光南說。<br />\n倪光南院士表示，在中國市場，盜版基本上市場上故意做的，微軟故意給你盜版。從Win7的開始，都是微軟允許你裝盜版，盜版的ID是一個ID，誰裝盜版，誰沒裝盜版，微軟都清楚。<br />\n倪光南稱，嚴格意義上說，不是盜版，是微軟的一個&ldquo;策略&rdquo;。微軟就是用盜版&ldquo;策略&rdquo;，故意免費讓中國用戶用，使中國人沒機會發展自己的操作系統，還反過來說中國人盜版，說中國人小偷。<br />\n&ldquo;互聯網公司APP都免費給用戶用，沒有互聯網公司說中國用戶是小偷。&rdquo;倪光南說。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t9ISrerOzW0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dt9ISrerOzW0&d=w%2FpB5ZNj24SnWsdMZ3SEwqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c6d2666e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t9ISrerOzW0</a><br />\n<br />\n點解有呢個世界會有一個國家可以無恥到咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ef953c57e05d3641da42dd6bfc35614f8bc0e2","tid":645523,"uid":61954,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"牛唔飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b938d99834caa6231a7cecf47f70ad804894d86e","tid":645523,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4f3daa18a69c1633a7fda8c4d61f26b016b90b","tid":645523,"uid":40445,"like":236,"dislike":0,"score":236,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:16:34.000Z","msg":"盜版不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;盜版！ &hellip;&hellip;中國人的事，能算偷麼？"},{"pid":"5c2147c698815e46f59a11f8b6d6ad6f086